Echo, as a TV miniseries, is the MCU's first foray into something more adult. With blood, action packed fight sequences, and dark tones, it hopes to introduce us to a different side of Maya Lopez then we've ever seen before. Marvel Netflix fans rejoice as we get the return of not one but 2 characters from Daredevil, just as it's been announced that the Marvel Netflix shows are canon. How will this affect the MCU as a whole? Check out this episode to find out!

